_text = "I open my eyes to see my friends looking back at me. The three of them are sitting around a picnic table, discussing plans for what to do after lunch.\n\nThey are all smiling and laughing. Without cell reception, it was just us. No distractions.\n\nThis was a trip that almost didn't happen. We all conveniently had the time off and decided last minute to go camping. My one friend told us she knew a place, and this soon turned out to be my favourite camping spot.\n\nI never went back there after this trip."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, FriendsLakeMemory, FriendsLakeMemory, false)
